	| Field          | Value       |
	| Name           | Common      |
	| Activity       | Phone       |
	| Shift category | Day         |
	| Start boundry  | 8:00-9:00   |
	| End boundry    | 17:00-18:00 |
	And there is a shift bag with
	| Field    | Value  |
	| Name     | Common |
